@startuml
title 中介者模式 (Mediator Pattern) - 聊天室系統

' --- 樣式設定 ---
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam monochrome false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

skinparam class {
BackgroundColor White
ArrowColor #d35400
BorderColor #e67e22
}

' --- 中介者介面 (Mediator Interface) ---
interface ChatMediator {
+ {abstract} sendMessage(msg: String, user: User): void
+ {abstract} addUser(user: User): void
}

' --- 具體中介者 (Concrete Mediator) ---
class ChatRoom implements ChatMediator {
- users: List
+ ChatRoom()
+ addUser(user: User): void
+ sendMessage(msg: String, user: User): void
}

' --- 抽象同事類別 (Colleague) ---
abstract class User {
# mediator: ChatMediator
# name: String
+ User(mediator: ChatMediator, name: String)
+ {abstract} send(msg: String): void
+ {abstract} receive(msg: String): void
}

' --- 具體同事類別 (Concrete Colleague) ---
class ChatUser extends User {
+ ChatUser(mediator: ChatMediator, name: String)
+ send(msg: String): void
+ receive(msg: String): void
}

' --- 關係連線 ---
' 中介者管理多個同事物件
ChatRoom o-- User : 管理 (Aggregation)

' 同事物件持有中介者的引用
User --> ChatMediator : 依賴通訊 (Association)

' --- 說明註解 ---
note left of ChatMediator : 中介者介面：\n定義了同事物件之間\n進行通訊的介面。

note right of ChatRoom : 具體中介者：\n協調各個同事物件的交互行為，\n它知道所有同事物件，\n並負責轉發訊息。

note top of User : 同事類別：\n每個同事只知道中介者，\n而不認識其他同事。

note bottom of ChatUser : 具體同事：\n透過中介者發送訊息，\n並接收來自中介者的訊息。

@enduml